  - 109
Format: Verse
By: Mechthild of Magdeburg
---
SOUL
But how can I support myself
If I must burden myself with thee?

LOVE
Ah! Unfaithful! He who has made the soul so noble
That it can enjoy nothing but God
Will never allow the body to want!
